    "statementHTML": "<div class=\"statement-body\">\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-goal\">\n   <h2><span class=\"icon icon-goal\">&nbsp;</span><span>Goal </span></h2>\n   <span class=\"question-statement\">In the Intergalactic Data Warehouse, you must compress package IDs before sending them through hyper-space.<br><br>To compress a package ID, replace each group of consecutive identical digits with the number of occurrences followed by the digit itself.<br><br><strong>Crucial:</strong> If the resulting compressed package ID is strictly longer than the original package ID, you must return the original one instead.</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"statement-section statement-protocol\">\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-input\"><strong>Line 1: </strong> A string <var>package_id</var> representing the package ID.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-output\">The compressed package ID, or <var>package_id</var> if the compressed package ID is longer.</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Constraints</div>\n      <div class=\"question-statement-constraints\">1 &le;  length of <var>package_id</var> &le; 100<br><var>package_id</var> contains only digits (0-9).</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"blk\">\n      <div class=\"title\">Example</div>\n      <div class=\"statement-inout\">\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-in\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Input</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-in\">22255</pre>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"statement-inout-out\">\n            <div class=\"title\">Output</div>\n            <pre class=\"question-statement-example-out\">3225</pre>\n         </div>\n      </div>\n   </div>\n</div>"
